This directory contains init scripts for running RapidSMS under Debian
 and Debian derived distros like Ubuntu.

The files are:
rapidsms-init.sh: start-up script for running a RapidSMS instance with 
                  PyGSM backend

rapidsms-spomsy-init.sh: start-up script for running a RapidSMS instance
                         with Spomskyd and Spomc backend.

rapidsms.cron: A cron job (to be placed in /etc/cron.d) that works
               with the init scripts to restart crashed RapidSMS
               instances

NOTE: See individual files for installation and usage instructions

